### Deploy on Render
1. Push this repo to GitHub
2. Create new Web Service on render.com
3. Set Start Command: `python app.py`
4. Set Environment Variable: `PORT=8000`
5. Open dashboard → Setup tab → Enter Angel One credentials

### Endpoints
- `/` — Main Dashboard
- `/ping` — Health check
- `/status` — Full system state (JSON)
- `/ccs` — CCS event log
- `/ws` — WebSocket

### Data Flow
Angel One WS → OI Data → L1-L13 Agents → CCS → L16 Contradiction → L15 Truth → L14 NAMBI → Decision → Telegram
